Package: cMut
Type: Package
Title: Identify clustered single nucleotide mutations and link to patterns
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Alex", "Janse", email = "alex.janse@radboudumc.nl", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: cMut is capable to find clustered single nucleotide variants and 
             link them to mutation patterns. 
             It also provide a stimulation function to determine the enrichment 
             of the found pattern results. Please, read the vignette and help 
             pages for more information.
License: GPL-3
